Indira Stefanianna https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Indira_Stefanianna 0 Indira Stefanianna (born Indira Stefanianna Christopherson; December 15, 1946), also credited as Indira Danks, Stefanianna Christopherson, and Indira Stefanianna, is an American singer and actress of Icelandic heritage, perhaps best known for her role as the original voice of Daphne Blake on Scooby-Doo, Where Are You! during its first (1969) season. Indira_Stefanianna ( born Indira_Stefanianna_Christopherson ; December_15_,_1946 ) , also_credited as Indira_Danks , Stefanianna_Christopherson , and Indira_Stefanianna , is an_American_singer_and_actress of Icelandic_heritage , perhaps_best_known for her_role as the_original_voice of Daphne_Blake on Scooby-Doo , Where Are You ! during its_first_(_1969_)_season .
